ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature of MAUREEN DOUGAN of Ottawa, Ontario, as Acting Director of the Canadian Museum of Nature to hold office during pleasure, effective October 4, 2010, in the place of Joanne V. DiCosimo, until such time as a Director is appointed.
